        <p class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white font-semibold">H.S. Johnson: Nine years. Still building.</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-slate-400 mt-1">UK watches and jewelry. 8 hours to 15 minutes. Under 1% compliance error rate.</p>
      </div>
